  "title": "Regional Sales Manager (Water Membrane Filtration)",
  "description": "<p><strong>About the Company:</strong></p><p>Our client is a Singapore-headquartered leader in advanced membrane technologies, develops and manufactures PVDF hollow fiber membranes for water and wastewater treatment, serving municipal utilities, industrial clients, and engineering solution providers across Southeast Asia.</p><p><strong>Responsibility:</strong></p><ul><li>Identify and develop new business opportunities within Singapore and neighboring markets.</li><li>Drive strategic partnerships and collaboration.</li><li>Work closely with the applications and engineering team to tailor solutions for customer needs.</li><li>Lead and execute global marketing campaigns, trade show participation, and product promotions.</li><li>Develop marketing materials including presentations, brochures, datasheets, and case studies.</li><li>Coordinate with global sales teams to ensure consistent branding and message delivery.</li><li>Manage digital marketing channels including website content, newsletters, and LinkedIn updates.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s degree in Environmental Engineering, Chemical Engineering, or a related field.</li><li>3 - 7 years’ experience in water treatment, membrane technology, or industrial equipment sales.</li><li>Strong technical understanding of MBR/UF membrane systems preferred.</li><li>Excellent communication, presentation, and proposal writing skills.</li><li>Proven ability to manage both customer-facing and internal coordination tasks effectively.</li><li>Ability to travel occasionally for exhibitions, customer  visits, or site support.</li><li>Experience in technical proposal writing and marketing communication is a strong plus</li></ul><p>Interested candidates please apply online or send your latest CV to <a href=\"mailto:alex.fong@AlwaysHired.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>alex.fong@AlwaysHired.com.sg</strong></a></p><p>AlwaysHired Pte Ltd</p><p>Reg No: R1549345</p><p>EA: 24C2293<br /></p><p><em>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. Please note that your response to this advertisement will constitute informed consent to the collection, use, and/or disclosure of personal data by AlwaysHired, its affiliates and, where necessary, to relevant third parties, for purposes such as job application processing, career advisory, research, and other administrative purposes, in compliance with the relevant provisions of the Privacy Policy available at www.alwayshired.com.sg/privacy-policy</em></p>",
